<body>

<p>
<b>IRC chat on <uri link="http://www.freenode.org/">Freenode</uri>:</b>.
</p>

<p>
The gentoo developers and helpers run the following channels for
mutual benefit, it is purely voluntary, and open to everyone. Feel
free to pop in and say Hello! Please keep the language clean in
#gentoo and #gentoo-dev. Owners of other Gentoo channels are permitted
to set their own policies relating to language usage. Additionally, please do not
bring bots into Gentoo channels without first consulting channel operators. This includes
bot-like scripts such as "seen" scripts.
</p>

